Package support

Class ConfigXML

  • java.lang.Object
    • support.ConfigXML

  • public class ConfigXML
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents system configuration contains: - email of the administrator - email password of the administrador - maximum jmetal evaluations - Path of the results file from the integer evaluation - Path of the results file from the integer evaluation - Path of the results file from the double evaluation - Path of the compiler .exe file to convert R file to EPS - Path of the R file - Path of the EPS environment variable - Path of the EPS file result (after compiling) - Path of the compiler .exe to convert Latex file to PDF - Path of the Latex file - Path of the PDF environment variable - Path of the PDF file result (after compiling)
    Author:
    Kevin Corrales nr 73529, Gustavo Morais nº 73036
